<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2010-06-08</DATELINE><TITLE>Challenges for Experimentation on Living Beings at the Dawn of the 21(st) Century</TITLE><BODY>“We can talk endlessly about moral progress, about social progress, about poetic progress, about progress made in happiness; nevertheless, there is a type of progress that defies any discussion, and that is scientific progress, as soon as we judge it within the hierarchy of knowledge, from a specifically intellectual point of view.”&#3;</BODY></TEXT>